    OpenPGP OpenPGP

    Email encryption. For all operating systems. Standing the test of time. 电子邮件加密。适用于所有操作系统。经得起时间的考验。

    Get OpenPGP Software获取 OpenPGP 软件

    OpenPGP is the most widely used email encryption standard. It is defined by the OpenPGP Working Group of the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF) as a Proposed Standard in RFC 4880. OpenPGP was originally derived from the PGP software, created by Phil Zimmermann.OpenPGP 是使用最广泛的电子邮件加密标准。它由 Internet 工程任务组 (IETF) 的 OpenPGP 工作组定义为 RFC 4880 中的建议标准。OpenPGP 最初源自 Phil Zimmermann 创建的 PGP 软件。

    Email encryption电子邮件加密

    Although OpenPGP’s main purpose is end-to-end encrypted email communication, it is also utilized for encrypted messaging and other use cases such as password managers.尽管 OpenPGP 的主要用途是端到端的加密电子邮件通信，但它也可用于加密消息传递和密码管理器等其他用例。

    About 关于

    OpenPGP is a non-proprietary format for authenticating or encrypting data, using public key cryptography.OpenPGP 是一种非专有格式，用于使用公钥密码术对数据进行身份验证或加密。

    It is based on the original PGP (Pretty Good Privacy) software.它基于原始的 PGP（Pretty Good Privacy）软件。

    Beginning in 1997, the OpenPGP Working Group was formed in the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF) to define this standard that had formerly been a proprietary product since 1991.从 1997 年开始，OpenPGP 工作组在互联网工程任务组 (IETF) 中成立，以定义该标准，该标准自 1991 年以来一直是专有产品。

    Over the past decade, PGP, and later OpenPGP, has become the standard for nearly all of the world’s signed or encrypted email.在过去十年中，PGP 以及后来的 OpenPGP 已成为全球几乎所有签名或加密电子邮件的标准。

    OpenPGP also defines a standard format for certificates which, unlike most other certificate formats, enables webs of trust.OpenPGP 还定义了证书的标准格式，与大多数其他证书格式不同，它支持信任网络。

    OpenPGP formats and uses are specified in many IETF RFCs and drafts1, so these standards can be implemented by any company without paying any licensing fees to anyone.许多 IETF RFC 和草案 1 中指定了 OpenPGP 格式和用途，因此任何公司都可以实施这些标准，而无需向任何人支付任何许可费用。

    1. RFC 3156 MIME Security with OpenPGP, RFC 4880 OpenPGP Message Format (the main one), RFC 5581 The Camellia Cipher in OpenPGP, RFC 6091 Using OpenPGP Keys for Transport Layer Security (TLS) Authentication, RFC 6637 Elliptic Curve Cryptography (ECC) in OpenPGP, and more. ↩RFC 3156 MIME Security with OpenPGP、RFC 4880 OpenPGP Message Format（主要的）、RFC 5581 The Camellia Cipher in OpenPGP、RFC 6091 Using OpenPGP keys for Transport Layer Security (TLS) Authentication、RFC 6637 OpenPGP 中的椭圆曲线密码术 (ECC) ， 和更多。 ↩

    History 历史

    OpenPGP is a non-proprietary protocol for encrypting email using public key cryptography. The OpenPGP protocol defines standard formats for encrypted messages, signatures, private keys, and certificates for exchanging public keys.OpenPGP 是一种非专有协议，用于使用公钥密码术对电子邮件进行加密。 OpenPGP 协议定义了加密消息、签名、私钥和用于交换公钥的证书的标准格式。

    It is based on the Pretty Good Privacy (PGP) freeware software as originally developed in 1991 by Phil Zimmermann. For that, he was the target of a three-year criminal investigation, because the US government held that US export restrictions for cryptographic software were violated when PGP spread all around the world following its publication as freeware.它基于 Phil Zimmermann 最初于 1991 年开发的 Pretty Good Privacy (PGP) 免费软件。为此，他成为了一项为期三年的刑事调查的目标，因为美国政府认为，当 PGP 作为免费软件发布到世界各地时，违反了美国对加密软件的出口限制。

    Despite the lack of funding, the lack of any paid staff, the lack of a company to stand behind it, and despite government persecution, PGP became the most widely used email encryption software in the world. After the government dropped its case in early 1996, Zimmermann founded PGP Inc. That company and its intellectual property were acquired by Network Associates Inc (NAI) in December 1997. NAI continued to own and develop PGP products for commercial and freeware purposes. In 2002, NAI discontinued development and sales of PGP, and sold the rights to it to a new company, PGP Corporation.尽管缺乏资金，没有任何带薪员工，没有公司支持，尽管受到政府的迫害，PGP 还是成为了世界上使用最广泛的电子邮件加密软件。在政府于 1996 年初撤销案件后，Zimmermann 创立了 PGP Inc。该公司及其知识产权于 1997 年 12 月被 Network Associates Inc (NAI) 收购。NAI 继续拥有和开发用于商业和免费软件目的的 PGP 产品。 2002 年，NAI 停止了 PGP 的开发和销售，并将其权利出售给了新公司 PGP Corporation。

    OpenPGP is the open standards version of NAI’s PGP encryption protocol. The OpenPGP Working Group is seeking the qualification of OpenPGP as an Internet Standard as defined by the IETF. Each distinct version of an Internet standards-related specification is published as part of the “Request for Comments” (RFC) document series.OpenPGP 是 NAI 的 PGP 加密协议的开放标准版本。 OpenPGP 工作组正在寻求 OpenPGP 作为 IETF 定义的互联网标准的资格。与 Internet 标准相关的规范的每个不同版本都作为“征求意见”(RFC) 文档系列的一部分发布。

    OpenPGP is on the Internet Standards Track and is under active development. Many e-mail clients provide OpenPGP-compliant email security as described in RFC 3156. The current specification is RFC 4880 (November 2007), the successor to RFC 2440. RFC 4880 specifies a suite of required algorithms consisting of ElGamal encryption, DSA, Triple DES and SHA-1. In addition to these algorithms, the standard recommends RSA as described in PKCS #1 v1.5 for encryption and signing, as well as AES-128, CAST-128 and IDEA. Beyond these, many other algorithms are supported. The standard was extended to support Camellia cipher by RFC 5581 in 2009, and encryption based on elliptic curve cryptography (ECDSA, ECDH) by RFC 6637 in 2012. Support of EdDSA will be added by draft-koch-eddsa-for-openpgp-00 proposed in 2014.OpenPGP 在 Internet 标准轨道上并且正在积极开发中。许多电子邮件客户端提供符合 OpenPGP 标准的电子邮件安全性，如 RFC 3156 中所述。当前规范是 RFC 4880（2007 年 11 月），它是 RFC 2440 的后继者。RFC 4880 指定了一套必需的算法，包括 ElGamal 加密、DSA、Triple DES 和 SHA-1。除了这些算法之外，该标准还推荐使用 PKCS #1 v1.5 中描述的 RSA 进行加密和签名，以及 AES-128、CAST-128 和 IDEA。除此之外，还支持许多其他算法。该标准在 2009 年通过 RFC 5581 扩展以支持 Camellia 密码，并在 2012 年通过 RFC 6637 扩展了基于椭圆曲线密码学（ECDSA、ECDH）的加密。draft-koch-eddsa-for-openpgp-00 将添加对 EdDSA 的支持2014 年提出。

    As far as we know, intelligence organizations aren’t able to break it.据我们所知，情报机构无法破解它。

    Learn more about the technical specifications of OpenPGP on our page about the standards.在我们关于标准的页面上了解更多关于 OpenPGP 技术规范的信息。

    Standard 标准

    The OpenPGP Proposed Standard is defined by the OpenPGP Working Group of the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF) in RFC 4880. This document contains all the necessary information to develop interoperable applications based on the OpenPGP format. It describes the format and methods needed to read, check, generate, and write conforming encrypted messages, keys, and signatures.OpenPGP 建议标准由互联网工程任务组 (IETF) 的 OpenPGP 工作组在 RFC 4880 中定义。该文档包含开发基于 OpenPGP 格式的可互操作应用程序的所有必要信息。它描述了读取、检查、生成和写入符合要求的加密消息、密钥和签名所需的格式和方法。

    Besides the message format specified in RFC 4880, a collection of other OpenPGP-related RFCs, XEPs, and, Internet Drafts have been written:除了 RFC 4880 中指定的消息格式外，还编写了一系列其他与 OpenPGP 相关的 RFC、XEP 和 Internet 草案：

    IETF RFCsIETF RFC

    • IETF OpenPGP Working GroupIETF OpenPGP 工作组
    • RFC 4880: OpenPGP Message FormatRFC 4880：OpenPGP 消息格式
    • RFC 3156: MIME Security with OpenPGPRFC 3156：使用 OpenPGP 的 MIME 安全性
    • RFC 6637: Elliptic Curve Cryptography (ECC) in OpenPGPRFC 6637：OpenPGP 中的椭圆曲线密码术 (ECC)
    • RFC 6091: Using OpenPGP Keys for Transport Layer Security (TLS) AuthenticationRFC 6091：使用 OpenPGP 密钥进行传输层安全 (TLS) 身份验证
    • RFC 5581: The Camellia Cipher in OpenPGPRFC 5581：OpenPGP 中的 Camellia 密码

    XMPP IntegrationXMPP 集成

    • XEP-0027 (obsolete)XEP-0027（过时）
    • XEP-0373: OpenPGP for XMPPXEP-0373：用于 XMPP 的 OpenPGP
    • XEP-0374: OpenPGP for XMPP Instant MessagingXEP-0374：用于 XMPP 即时消息的 OpenPGP

    Current Internet Drafts当前的互联网草稿

    • The OpenPGP HTTP Keyserver Protocol (HKP)OpenPGP HTTP 密钥服务器协议 (HKP)
    • Using DANE to Associate OpenPGP public keys with email addresses使用 DANE 将 OpenPGP 公钥与电子邮件地址相关联
    • Best Common Practise for using OPENPGPKEY records使用 OPENPGPKEY 记录的最佳常见做法
    • Media type literal packet in OpenPGPOpenPGP 中的媒体类型文字包
    • EdDSA for OpenPGP用于 OpenPGP 的 EdDSA

    • URI Attributes for OpenPGPOpenPGP 的 URI 属性
    • Modernizing the OpenPGP Message Format使 OpenPGP 消息格式现代化
    • Forward Secrecy Extensions for OpenPGPOpenPGP 的前向保密扩展
    • OpenPGP Extensions for Device Certificates设备证书的 OpenPGP 扩展
    • The OpenPGP Message FormatOpenPGP 消息格式
    • The “OpenPGP” mail and news header field“OpenPGP”邮件和新闻标题字段

    Obsolete RFCs过时的 RFC

    Webmail Provider with In-Browser Cryptography具有浏览器内加密的网络邮件提供商

    In contrast to the previous section, the following webmail providers do not require the installation of additional browser plugins, instead OpenPGP is implemented in JavaScript provided directly by the website. While these are easier to set up and provide basic security guarantees with OpenPGP, some people don’t consider these “end-to-end secure”.与上一节相比，以下网络邮件提供商不需要安装额外的浏览器插件，OpenPGP 是在网站直接提供的 JavaScript 中实现的。虽然使用 OpenPGP 更容易设置并提供基本的安全保证，但有些人并不认为这些是“端到端安全的”。

    GPGFrontend GPGFrontend

    GpgFrontend is a modern, easy-to-use, compact, cross-platform, and installation-free gpg front-end tool. By using GpgFrontend, you can quickly encrypt and decrypt text or files. Or at the same time as the above operations, you can add your own signature to let others know that this document or this paragraph of text was issued by you.GpgFrontend 是一个现代的、易于使用的、紧凑的、跨平台的、免安装的 gpg 前端工具。通过使用 GpgFrontend，您可以快速加密和解密文本或文件。或者在进行上述操作的同时，您可以加上自己的签名，让别人知道这份文件或这段文字是您签发的。

    Furthermore, it visualizes most of the common operations of gpg commands. It aims to allow ordinary users to quickly use gpg and make professional users more convenient. GpgFrontend supports some new features of OpenPGP.此外，它还可视化了 gpg 命令的大部分常见操作。旨在让普通用户快速使用gpg，让专业用户更方便。 GpgFrontend 支持 OpenPGP 的一些新特性。

    Features:特征：

    • Open source, free, no need to install.开源，免费，无需安装。
    • Can run on Windows, Linux and macOS.可以在 Windows、Linux 和 macOS 上运行。
    • Just double-click, and then you can use it freely.只需双击，即可自由使用。
    • Before use, you only need to install gnupg. A tiny tool of a few MB.使用前，你只需要安装gnupg。几 MB 的小工具。
    • Supports multiple languages. Don’t forget to help me translate this software.支持多种语言。别忘了帮我翻译这个软件。
